    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074868_42_410-427",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "410-427",
      "markText": "“人的年纪越大，越会变回小孩子。”",
      "totalCount": 1668,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074868&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=410&rangeEnd=427",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78632b80813ab83beg0181c3?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=410&rangeEnd=427"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074868_46_11584-11645",
      "chapterUid": 46,
      "range": "11584-11645",
      "markText": "我为自己感到自豪，我为自己感到骄傲，我对爱我的那个人有信心。任何陌生人的流言都无法撼动我的安全。我是一个实现了自我的女性。",
      "totalCount": 1224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074868&chapterUid=46&rangeStart=11584&rangeEnd=11645",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78632b80813ab83beg0181c3?chapterUid=46&rangeStart=11584&rangeEnd=11645"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074868_41_372-432",
      "chapterUid": 41,
      "range": "372-432",
      "markText": "一个民族的青春在于芸芸老者。 ——切萨雷·帕韦泽",
      "totalCount": 1207,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074868&chapterUid=41&rangeStart=372&rangeEnd=432",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78632b80813ab83beg0181c3?chapterUid=41&rangeStart=372&rangeEnd=432"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074868_51_703-768",
      "chapterUid": 51,
      "range": "703-768",
      "markText": "我唯一过敏的正是那些整天不停抱怨的人，我感觉他们有毒。每个人都有各自的烦恼，年岁越大，烦恼越多，可是不停地罗列那些又有什么意义呢？",
      "totalCount": 1200,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074868&chapterUid=51&rangeStart=703&rangeEnd=768",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78632b80813ab83beg0181c3?chapterUid=51&rangeStart=703&rangeEnd=768"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074868_44_10750-10783",
      "chapterUid": 44,
      "range": "10750-10783",
      "markText": "家庭的价值是由每个家庭成员的幸福总和决定的，而不是银行账户里的钱。",
      "totalCount": 1199,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074868&chapterUid=44&rangeStart=10750&rangeEnd=10783",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78632b80813ab83beg0181c3?chapterUid=44&rangeStart=10750&rangeEnd=10783"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074868_47_1826-1852",
      "chapterUid": 47,
      "range": "1826-1852",
      "markText": "我们婚姻的秘诀正是如此：永不放弃自己想要成为的样子。",
      "totalCount": 1184,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074868&chapterUid=47&rangeStart=1826&rangeEnd=1852",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78632b80813ab83beg0181c3?chapterUid=47&rangeStart=1826&rangeEnd=1852"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074868_41_1106-1159",
      "chapterUid": 41,
      "range": "1106-1159",
      "markText": "我深信，智慧的火焰是唯一能够照亮困境的光芒，唯有这样的能量源泉能够在时间的流逝中滋养自我，而不被消耗殆尽。",
      "totalCount": 1170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074868&chapterUid=41&rangeStart=1106&rangeEnd=1159",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78632b80813ab83beg0181c3?chapterUid=41&rangeStart=1106&rangeEnd=1159"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074868_44_18433-18490",
      "chapterUid": 44,
      "range": "18433-18490",
      "markText": "如果相爱的两人认出了对方，就能永远找到彼此。我等你，阿尔多。",
      "totalCount": 1152,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074868&chapterUid=44&rangeStart=18433&rangeEnd=18490",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78632b80813ab83beg0181c3?chapterUid=44&rangeStart=18433&rangeEnd=18490"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074868_42_5649-5695",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "5649-5695",
      "markText": "狗宝宝们教会我一个最好的方法，那就是通过一个人对待动物的方式去评判他，以防将来对这个人失望。",
      "totalCount": 1128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074868&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=5649&rangeEnd=5695",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78632b80813ab83beg0181c3?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=5649&rangeEnd=5695"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074868_43_16591-16617",
      "chapterUid": 43,
      "range": "16591-16617",
      "markText": "金钱来了又去；可若失去了自由，生命便再也没有了价值。",
      "totalCount": 1040,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074868&chapterUid=43&rangeStart=16591&rangeEnd=16617",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78632b80813ab83beg0181c3?chapterUid=43&rangeStart=16591&rangeEnd=16617"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074868_48_2551-2593",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "2551-2593",
      "markText": "子女永远无法为父母的死亡做好准备，而且世界上没有任何一种痛苦能够训练你承受这种悲痛。",
      "totalCount": 1026,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074868&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=2551&rangeEnd=2593",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78632b80813ab83beg0181c3?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=2551&rangeEnd=2593"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074868_41_1188-1252",
      "chapterUid": 41,
      "range": "1188-1252",
      "markText": "智慧也是唯一一座能够指引你从黑暗大海驶向光明海岸的灯塔。在这个过程中，承受多少苦难并不重要，重要的是你终止痛苦的愿望有多么强烈。",
      "totalCount": 1001,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074868&chapterUid=41&rangeStart=1188&rangeEnd=1252",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78632b80813ab83beg0181c3?chapterUid=41&rangeStart=1188&rangeEnd=1252"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074868_44_10956-10981",
      "chapterUid": 44,
      "range": "10956-10981",
      "markText": "如果我自己都不能幸福，那么拥有伴侣也不会获得幸福。",
      "totalCount": 975,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074868&chapterUid=44&rangeStart=10956&rangeEnd=10981",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78632b80813ab83beg0181c3?chapterUid=44&rangeStart=10956&rangeEnd=10981"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074868_43_11649-11701",
      "chapterUid": 43,
      "range": "11649-11701",
      "markText": "小姨莉迪亚教我如何培养自己的女性气质。她告诉我，要将它视为一种馈赠，而且要悉心照料自己以作为对它的感谢。",
